Shortshorts
===========

Make your models show some skin.



script/generate shortshorts_migration
rake db:migrate


Routes:
map.shortshorts




Example
=======



You can put all short urls into a subdirectory by specifying a string in Routes:
map.shortshorts "i"    # creates: http://example.com/i/4ZPn




